&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(40, 40, 40);&quot;&gt;About Us&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Our leading SaaS-based Global Employment Platform™ enables clients to expand into over 180 countries quickly and efficiently, without the complexities of establishing local entities. At G-P, we’re dedicated to breaking down barriers to global business and creating opportunities for everyone, everywhere.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Our diverse, remote-first teams are essential to our success. We empower our Dream Team members with flexibility and resources, fostering an environment where innovation thrives and every contribution is valued and celebrated.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;The work you do here will positively impact lives around the world. We stand by our promise: Opportunity Made Possible. In addition to competitive compensation and benefits, we invite you to join us in expanding your skills and helping to reshape the future of work.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;At G-P, we assist organizations in building exceptional global teams in days, not months—streamlining the hiring, onboarding, and management process to unlock growth potential for all.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;About this Position&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;G-P has a fantastic opportunity for a 3rd year student to participate in a 12 week, paid summer internship, within the Software Engineering team. We&#39;re seeking interns with creative minds and software engineering expertise like yours to bring fresh ideas to G-P and help us build the next generation technology. Join the team that is helping companies change the way the world works, eliminating barriers to global business!&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;As the leader in the Employer of Record industry, our focus at G-P is on GROWTH – the growth of our customers, our business, and our people. We are committed to providing our interns with opportunities for success and growth to advance their careers.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;As an intern, you will collaborate closely with our software engineering mentors on either an existing team or a new project. You&#39;ll do work that really matters while gaining hands-on, practical software engineering experience. Our interns are fully-integrated Software Engineers who will spend the summer putting academic knowledge into real-time technical projects.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will do:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Contribute to the design and development of our cloud-enabled products, working on all&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;parts of the code stack&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Learn cutting edge technologies under the guidance of our expert development teams who will develop your skills and help you grow&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Be mentored by software engineers who are passionate about development&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Gain exposure to different functional areas within the business&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we are looking for:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em data-renderer-mark=&quot;true&quot;&gt;Minimum Requirements:&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You are in the 3rd year of your bachelor’s degree in Computer Science, Computer&amp;nbsp; Engineering, or related fields.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You have a solid foundation in CS theory and exceptional programming and design skills&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You possess a love for technology and can explain your college and personal projects.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You are genuinely interested in Globalization Partners and are eager to benefit from the&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;invaluable expertise of our technical team.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;line-height: 1.5;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What we can offer you:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Experience working on impactful and exciting real-time projects in an agile environment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Integrate into a team environment providing an opportunity to meet new colleagues,&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;mentors, and gain access to networking opportunities.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;A fun place to work&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
